---
import Mascot from '../Mascot.astro';
---
<section class="slide slide-call-stack">
  <div class="content">
    <h2 class="title">El Call Stack <span class="subtitle-inline">(Pila de llamadas)</span></h2>

    <div class="main-grid">
      <div class="stack-visual" aria-label="Diagrama de pila de llamadas con funciones apiladas">
        <div class="stack-label">Call Stack</div>
        <div class="stack-container">
          <div class="stack-frame frame-3">
            <span class="frame-name">multiplicar()</span>
            <span class="frame-tag">3°</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-frame frame-2">
            <span class="frame-name">calcular()</span>
            <span class="frame-tag">2°</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-frame frame-1">
            <span class="frame-name">main()</span>
            <span class="frame-tag">1°</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-base">
          <span>← Base de la pila</span>
        </div>

        <svg class="lifo-arrow" viewBox="0 0 60 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <text x="30" y="14" text-anchor="middle" fill="#3B82F6" font-size="9" font-weight="bold">ENTRA</text>
          <path d="M30 18 L30 50" stroke="#3B82F6" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowDown)"/>
          <text x="30" y="75" text-anchor="middle" fill="#8B5CF6" font-size="9" font-weight="bold">SALE</text>
          <path d="M30 80 L30 112" stroke="#8B5CF6" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowUp)"/>
          <defs>
            <marker id="arrowDown" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="3" refY="6" orient="auto">
              <path d="M0,0 L3,6 L6,0 Z" fill="#3B82F6"/>
            </marker>
            <marker id="arrowUp" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="3" refY="0" orient="auto">
              <path d="M0,6 L3,0 L6,6 Z" fill="#8B5CF6"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="explanation">
        <div class="description-card">
          <p class="description">
            Es como una pila de platos. El último que entra es el primero en salir
            <strong>(LIFO — Last In, First Out)</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">1</span>
            <p>Cuando llamas a una función, se <strong>apila</strong> encima de la pila.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">2</span>
            <p>Si esa función llama a otra, la nueva se apila <strong>encima</strong>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">3</span>
            <p>Cuando una función termina, se <strong>desapila</strong> y el control vuelve a la anterior.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">4</span>
            <p>Si la pila se vacía, JavaScript está <strong>libre</strong> para procesar la siguiente tarea.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Mascot message="Piensa en mí como la pila: el último en entrar es el primero en salir. ¡LIFO!" mood="thinking" />
</section>

<style>
  .slide-call-stack {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, var(--color-call-stack-bg) 0%, var(--color-bg) 60%);
  }

  .content {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 860px;
    padding: var(--space-8);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-call-stack);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .subtitle-inline {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .main-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Stack visual */
  .stack-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .stack-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-call-stack);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .stack-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column-reverse;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .stack-frame {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-call-stack);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    animation: slideIn 0.4s ease both;
  }

  .frame-1 { background: #1D3461; color: #93C5FD; animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .frame-2 { background: #1e3a6e; color: #60A5FA; animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .frame-3 { background: #1e4080; color: #3B82F6; animation-delay: 0.4s; }

  @keyframes slideIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .frame-tag {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .stack-base {
    width: 100%;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--color-call-stack);
    padding-top: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .lifo-arrow {
    width: 60px;
    height: 120px;
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }

  /* Explanation */
  .explanation {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .description-card {
    background: var(--color-call-stack-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-call-stack);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-4);
  }

  .description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .description strong {
    color: var(--color-call-stack);
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
  }

  .step-num {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-call-stack);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .step strong {
    color: var(--color-call-stack);
  }
</style>
